        </div>
    </div>
</div>
                        
                        <p>Nonetheless, Lehrer added that collegiate Quidditch is “not just about the ‘The Boy Who Lived.’”</p>
<p>“None of us are really Harry Potter experts or whatever,” Lehrer said. “It's more that it's a really fun game and nothing like it is really done—it’s kind of handball-ish and kind of dodgeball-ish and kind of tag-ish. It’s unique and entertaining and anyone can play.”</p>

